data.title: Pacific Lutheran University Athletics
data.meta_description: David Fisher - College: Ran on the 4x100-meter team that finished fourth and the 4x400-meter team that finished first at the NWC Championships in 2011... formerly
data.text:
College: Ran on the 4x100-meter team that finished fourth and the 4x400-meter team that finished first at the NWC Championships in 2011... formerly a member of PLU football team.

High School: Academic All-State for football and track... all-league honors for football... perseverance award for track... Set "Tiger Run" school record for football... team captain for football... Sertoma Northern Region All-Star for football.

Personal: Majoring in Health and Fitness and minoring in Sports Psychology... son of John, who played football at Univ. of Nevada at Reno, and Jocelyn, who ran track... born on September 24, 1990... brother to Daniel, 24, and Dusty, 18.
